      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is a true standout \u2014 meticulously maintained and presented in flawless, turn-key condition. Every surface gleams, the interior is spotless and free of wear, and the mechanicals have been carefully serviced to ensure peak performance. This is the rare find that needs absolutely nothing: no repairs, no reconditioning, just pure driving pleasure from day one. Serious buyers who demand the very best will not be disappointed. Come see it in person \u2014 it speaks for itself.",
      "price": 46000.0,
